{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":599,"text":"I've learned some of\nmy most important life lessons"},{"time":5380,"text":"from drug dealers"},{"time":7879,"text":"and gang members"},{"time":10250,"text":"and prostitutes,"},{"time":12503,"text":"and I've had some of my most\nprofound theological conversations"},{"time":18130,"text":"not in the hallowed halls of a seminary"},{"time":21704,"text":"but on a street corner"},{"time":24120,"text":"on a Friday night, at 1 a.m."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27701,"text":"That's a little unusual, since I am\na Baptist minister, seminary-trained,"},{"time":33872,"text":"and pastored a church for over 20 years,"},{"time":38226,"text":"but it's true."},{"time":40594,"text":"It came as a part of my participation"},{"time":43264,"text":"in a public safety\ncrime reduction strategy"},{"time":47490,"text":"that saw a 79 percent reduction\nin violent crime"},{"time":51247,"text":"over an eight-year period in a major city."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55385,"text":"But I didn't start out wanting to be\n"},{"time":57242,"text":"a part of somebody's\ncrime reduction strategy."},{"time":61335,"text":"I was 25, had my first church."},{"time":64220,"text":"If you would have asked me\nwhat my ambition was,"},{"time":66600,"text":"I would have told you\nI wanted to be a megachurch pastor."},{"time":70918,"text":"I wanted a 15-, 20,000-member church."},{"time":74865,"text":"I wanted my own television ministry."},{"time":77675,"text":"I wanted my own clothing line."},{"time":80391,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":81747,"text":"I wanted to be your long distance carrier."},{"time":83888,"text":"You know, the whole nine yards."},{"time":85732,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":88425,"text":"After about a year of pastoring,"},{"time":91478,"text":"my membership went up about 20 members."},{"time":95100,"text":"So megachurchdom was way down the road."},{"time":98730,"text":"But seriously, if you'd have said,\n\"What is your ambition?\""},{"time":101554,"text":"I would have said just to be\na good pastor,"},{"time":103575,"text":"to be able to be with people\nthrough all the passages of life,"},{"time":107940,"text":"to preach messages that would have\nan everyday meaning for folks,"},{"time":112213,"text":"and in the African-American tradition,"},{"time":115115,"text":"to be able to represent\nthe community that I serve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119265,"text":"But there was something else\nthat was happening in my city"},{"time":124333,"text":"and in the entire metro area,"},{"time":126364,"text":"and in most metro areas\nin the United States,"},{"time":130125,"text":"and that was the homicide rate\nstarted to rise precipitously."},{"time":135534,"text":"And there were young people\nwho were killing each other"},{"time":138101,"text":"for reasons that I thought\nwere very trivial,"},{"time":140748,"text":"like bumping into someone\nin a high school hallway,"},{"time":145652,"text":"and then after school,\nshooting the person."},{"time":148921,"text":"Someone with the wrong color shirt on,"},{"time":152427,"text":"on the wrong street corner\nat the wrong time."},{"time":156630,"text":"And something needed\nto be done about that."},{"time":160548,"text":"It got to the point where it started\nto change the character of the city."},{"time":164872,"text":"You could go to any housing project,"},{"time":167100,"text":"for example, like the one that was\ndown the street from my church,"},{"time":170259,"text":"and you would walk in,\nand it would be like a ghost town,"},{"time":173161,"text":"because the parents wouldn't allow\ntheir kids to come out and play,"},{"time":176783,"text":"even in the summertime,\nbecause of the violence."},{"time":179847,"text":"You would listen in the neighborhoods\non any given night,"},{"time":182599,"text":"and to the untrained ear,\nit sounded like fireworks,"},{"time":185827,"text":"but it was gunfire."},{"time":187207,"text":"You'd hear it almost every night,\nwhen you were cooking dinner,"},{"time":191040,"text":"telling your child a bedtime story,\nor just watching TV."},{"time":196200,"text":"And you can go to any emergency\nroom at any hospital,"},{"time":200994,"text":"and you would see lying on gurneys"},{"time":204123,"text":"young black and Latino men\nshot and dying."},{"time":208697,"text":"And I was doing funerals,"},{"time":210532,"text":"but not of the venerated matriarchs\nand patriarchs who'd lived a long life"},{"time":214990,"text":"and there's a lot to say."},{"time":217892,"text":"I was doing funerals of 18-year-olds,"},{"time":220748,"text":"17-year-olds,"},{"time":222710,"text":"and 16-year-olds,"},{"time":224614,"text":"and I was standing in a church\nor at a funeral home"},{"time":229281,"text":"struggling to say something"},{"time":231405,"text":"that would make some meaningful impact."},{"time":235300,"text":"And so while my colleagues were building\nthese cathedrals great and tall"},{"time":241290,"text":"and buying property outside of the city"},{"time":244628,"text":"and moving their congregations out"},{"time":247198,"text":"so that they could create\nor recreate their cities of God,"},{"time":252337,"text":"the social structures in the inner cities"},{"time":255494,"text":"were sagging under the weight\nof all of this violence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259411,"text":"And so I stayed, because somebody\nneeded to do something,"},{"time":262298,"text":"and so I had looked at what I had\nand moved on that."},{"time":265850,"text":"I started to preach decrying\nthe violence in the community."},{"time":270192,"text":"And I started to look\nat the programming in my church,"},{"time":272746,"text":"and I started to build programs\nthat would catch the at-risk youth,"},{"time":276647,"text":"those who were on the fence\nto the violence."},{"time":280106,"text":"I even tried to be innovative\nin my preaching."},{"time":282266,"text":"You all have heard of rap music, right?"},{"time":284495,"text":"Rap music?"},{"time":285725,"text":"I even tried to rap sermon one time."},{"time":288303,"text":"It didn't work, but at least I tried it."},{"time":292038,"text":"I'll never forget the young person\nwho came to me after that sermon."},{"time":296244,"text":"He waited until everybody was gone,"},{"time":298124,"text":"and he said, \"Rev, rap sermon, huh?\"\nAnd I was like, \"Yeah, what do you think?\""},{"time":301956,"text":"And he said, \"Don't do that again, Rev.\""},{"time":304997,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":308132,"text":"But I preached and I built these programs,"},{"time":310465,"text":"and I thought maybe if\nmy colleagues did the same"},{"time":312903,"text":"that it would make a difference."},{"time":315109,"text":"But the violence just\ncareened out of control,"},{"time":319100,"text":"and people who were not involved in\nthe violence were getting shot and killed:"},{"time":323833,"text":"somebody going to buy a pack\nof cigarettes at a convenience store,"},{"time":329662,"text":"or someone who was sitting\nat a bus stop just waiting for a bus,"},{"time":333661,"text":"or kids who were playing in the park,"},{"time":335820,"text":"oblivious to the violence\non the other side of the park,"},{"time":339117,"text":"but it coming and visiting them."},{"time":341811,"text":"Things were out of control,"},{"time":344365,"text":"and I didn't know what to do,"},{"time":346803,"text":"and then something happened\nthat changed everything for me."},{"time":351795,"text":"It was a kid by the name of Jesse McKie,"},{"time":354720,"text":"walking home with his friend\nRigoberto Carrion"},{"time":357646,"text":"to the housing project\ndown the street from my church."},{"time":361350,"text":"They met up with a group of youth\nwho were from a gang in Dorchester,"},{"time":365749,"text":"and they were killed."},{"time":368120,"text":"But as Jesse was running\nfrom the scene mortally wounded,"},{"time":370880,"text":"he was running in the direction\nof my church,"},{"time":373249,"text":"and he died some 100, 150 yards away."},{"time":376657,"text":"If he would have gotten to the church,\nit wouldn't have made a difference,"},{"time":380196,"text":"because the lights were out;\nnobody was home."},{"time":383077,"text":"And I took that as a sign."},{"time":386230,"text":"When they caught some of the youth\nthat had done this deed,"},{"time":389235,"text":"to my surprise, they were around my age,"},{"time":392903,"text":"but the gulf that was between us was vast."},{"time":396525,"text":"It was like we were in two\ncompletely different worlds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":400728,"text":"And so as I contemplated all of this"},{"time":403730,"text":"and looked at what was happening,"},{"time":406138,"text":"I suddenly realized that there was\na paradox that was emerging inside of me,"},{"time":412420,"text":"and the paradox was this:\nin all of those sermons"},{"time":414836,"text":"that I preached decrying the violence,"},{"time":416819,"text":"I was also talking about\nbuilding community,"},{"time":421161,"text":"but I suddenly realized"},{"time":423343,"text":"that there was a certain\nsegment of the population"},{"time":426432,"text":"that I was not including\nin my definition of community."},{"time":430621,"text":"And so the paradox was this:"},{"time":432020,"text":"If I really wanted the community\nthat I was preaching for,"},{"time":435719,"text":"I needed to reach out"},{"time":437739,"text":"and embrace this group\nthat I had cut out of my definition."},{"time":442912,"text":"Which meant not about building programs"},{"time":445529,"text":"to catch those who were\non the fences of violence,"},{"time":449128,"text":"but to reach out and to embrace those\nwho were committing the acts of violence,"},{"time":454160,"text":"the gang bangers, the drug dealers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456906,"text":"As soon as I came to that realization,\na quick question came to my mind."},{"time":461494,"text":"Why me?"},{"time":463358,"text":"I mean, isn't this a law\nenforcement issue?"},{"time":465403,"text":"This is why we have the police, right?"},{"time":468233,"text":"As soon as the question, \"Why me?\" came,\nthe answer came just as quickly:"},{"time":472969,"text":"Why me? Because I'm the one who\ncan't sleep at night thinking about it."},{"time":478666,"text":"Because I'm the one looking around saying\nsomebody needs to do something about this,"},{"time":482853,"text":"and I'm starting to realize\nthat that someone is me."},{"time":486367,"text":"I mean, isn't that how\nmovements start anyway?"},{"time":488692,"text":"They don't start with a grand convention\nand people coming together"},{"time":492926,"text":"and then walking in lockstep\nwith a statement."},{"time":496749,"text":"But it starts with just a few,\nor maybe just one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":501924,"text":"It started with me that way,"},{"time":504075,"text":"and so I decided to figure out\nthe culture of violence"},{"time":508430,"text":"in which these young people\nwho were committing them existed,"},{"time":511301,"text":"and I started to volunteer\nat the high school."},{"time":513475,"text":"After about two weeks\nof volunteering at the high school,"},{"time":516170,"text":"I realized that the youth\nthat I was trying to reach,"},{"time":518655,"text":"they weren't going to high school."},{"time":521102,"text":"I started to walk in the community,"},{"time":523801,"text":"and it didn't take a rocket scientist\nto realize that they weren't out"},{"time":527189,"text":"during the day."},{"time":529836,"text":"So I started to walk the streets\nat night, late at night,"},{"time":534471,"text":"going into the parks where they were,"},{"time":537110,"text":"building the relationship\nthat was necessary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":540238,"text":"A tragedy happened in Boston\nthat brought a number of clergy together,"},{"time":545210,"text":"and there was a small cadre of us\nwho came to the realization"},{"time":549204,"text":"that we had to come out\nof the four walls of our sanctuary"},{"time":552189,"text":"and meet the youth where they were,"},{"time":553868,"text":"and not try to figure out\nhow to bring them in."},{"time":557735,"text":"And so we decided to walk together,"},{"time":560439,"text":"and we would get together"},{"time":562420,"text":"in one of the most dangerous\nneighborhoods in the city"},{"time":565152,"text":"on a Friday night and on a Saturday night"},{"time":567567,"text":"at 10 p.m.,"},{"time":569529,"text":"and we would walk\nuntil 2 or 3 in the morning."},{"time":572390,"text":"I imagine we were quite the anomaly\nwhen we first started walking."},{"time":575612,"text":"I mean, we weren't drug dealers."},{"time":577934,"text":"We weren't drug customers."},{"time":579809,"text":"We weren't the police. Some of us\nwould have collars on."},{"time":582566,"text":"It was probably a really odd thing."},{"time":585143,"text":"But they started speaking\nto us after a while,"},{"time":588347,"text":"and what we found out is that"},{"time":590274,"text":"while we were walking,\nthey were watching us,"},{"time":593963,"text":"and they wanted to make sure\nof a couple of things:"},{"time":596500,"text":"that number one, we were going\nto be consistent in our behavior,"},{"time":601671,"text":"that we would keep coming out there;"},{"time":603384,"text":"and then secondly,\nthey had wanted to make sure"},{"time":605575,"text":"that we weren't out there to exploit them."},{"time":608130,"text":"Because there was always\nsomebody who would say,"},{"time":610410,"text":"\"We're going to take back the streets,\""},{"time":612274,"text":"but they would always seem to have\na television camera with them,"},{"time":615398,"text":"or a reporter,"},{"time":617231,"text":"and they would enhance\ntheir own reputation"},{"time":619739,"text":"to the detriment of those on the streets."},{"time":622246,"text":"So when they saw that we had none of that,"},{"time":624801,"text":"they decided to talk to us."},{"time":627400,"text":"And then we did\nan amazing thing for preachers."},{"time":631255,"text":"We decided to listen and not preach."},{"time":635352,"text":"Come on, give it up for me."},{"time":637223,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":640682,"text":"All right, come on, you're cutting\ninto my time now, okay? (Laughter)"},{"time":644792,"text":"But it was amazing."},{"time":646612,"text":"We said to them, \"We don't know\nour own communities after 9 p.m. at night,"},{"time":652919,"text":"between 9 p.m. and 5 a.m.,"},{"time":655759,"text":"but you do."},{"time":657389,"text":"You are the subject matter experts,\nif you will, of that period of time."},{"time":662551,"text":"So talk to us. Teach us."},{"time":665387,"text":"Help us to see what we're not seeing."},{"time":667477,"text":"Help us to understand\nwhat we're not understanding.\""},{"time":671262,"text":"And they were all too happy to do that,"},{"time":673677,"text":"and we got an idea of what life\non the streets was all about,"},{"time":678436,"text":"very different than what you see\non the 11 o'clock news,"},{"time":682244,"text":"very different than what is portrayed\nin popular media and even social media."}]},{"cues":[{"time":688480,"text":"And as we were talking with them,"},{"time":690696,"text":"a number of myths were dispelled\nabout them with us."},{"time":694899,"text":"And one of the biggest myths was\nthat these kids were cold and heartless"},{"time":701576,"text":"and uncharacteristically bold\nin their violence."},{"time":705440,"text":"What we found out was the exact opposite."},{"time":708737,"text":"Most of the young people\nwho were out there on the streets"},{"time":711477,"text":"are just trying to make it on the streets."},{"time":714542,"text":"And we also found out"},{"time":716492,"text":"that some of the most\nintelligent and creative"},{"time":720052,"text":"and magnificent and wise"},{"time":726979,"text":"people that we've ever met"},{"time":729472,"text":"were on the street,\nengaged in a struggle."},{"time":734247,"text":"And I know some of them call it survival,\nbut I call them overcomers,"},{"time":738390,"text":"because when you're in\nthe conditions that they're in,"},{"time":741430,"text":"to be able to live every day\nis an accomplishment of overcoming."},{"time":747669,"text":"And as a result of that, we said to them,"},{"time":749823,"text":"\"How do you see this church,\nhow do you see this institution"},{"time":753271,"text":"helping this situation?\""},{"time":756312,"text":"And we developed a plan\nin conversation with these youths."},{"time":760610,"text":"We stopped looking at them\nas the problem to be solved,"},{"time":764764,"text":"and we started looking at them\nas partners, as assets,"},{"time":769942,"text":"as co-laborers in the struggle\nto reduce violence in the community."},{"time":775654,"text":"Imagine developing a plan,"},{"time":777836,"text":"you have one minister at one table\nand a heroin dealer at the other table,"},{"time":782945,"text":"coming up with a way in which the church\ncan help the entire community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":789510,"text":"The Boston Miracle was about\nbringing people together."},{"time":793788,"text":"We had other partners."},{"time":795645,"text":"We had law enforcement partners."},{"time":797248,"text":"We had police officers."},{"time":800160,"text":"It wasn't the entire force,"},{"time":802310,"text":"because there were still some who still\nhad that lock-'em-up mentality,"},{"time":807000,"text":"but there were other cops"},{"time":809136,"text":"who saw the honor in partnering\nwith the community,"},{"time":814221,"text":"who saw the responsibility from themselves"},{"time":817407,"text":"to be able to work as partners\nwith community leaders and faith leaders"},{"time":823960,"text":"in order to reduce violence\nin the community."},{"time":826490,"text":"Same with probation officers,"},{"time":828941,"text":"same with judges,"},{"time":830822,"text":"same with folks who were\nup that law enforcement chain,"},{"time":834560,"text":"because they realized, like we did,"},{"time":836743,"text":"that we'll never arrest ourselves\nout of this situation,"},{"time":840435,"text":"that there will not be\nenough prosecutions made,"},{"time":846314,"text":"and you cannot fill these jails up enough"},{"time":851762,"text":"in order to alleviate the problem."},{"time":855897,"text":"I helped to start an organization"},{"time":859637,"text":"20 years ago, a faith-based organization,\nto deal with this issue."},{"time":864443,"text":"I left it about four years ago"},{"time":867740,"text":"and started working in cities\nacross the United States,"},{"time":870840,"text":"19 in total,"},{"time":872779,"text":"and what I found out\nwas that in those cities,"},{"time":875599,"text":"there was always this component\nof community leaders"},{"time":880429,"text":"who put their heads down\nand their nose to the grindstone,"},{"time":884724,"text":"who checked their egos at the door"},{"time":887690,"text":"and saw the whole as greater\nthan the sum of its parts,"},{"time":890947,"text":"and came together and found ways\nto work with youth out on the streets,"},{"time":896566,"text":"that the solution is not more cops,"},{"time":901349,"text":"but the solution is mining the assets\nthat are there in the community,"},{"time":906643,"text":"to have a strong community component"},{"time":910381,"text":"in the collaboration\naround violence reduction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":915373,"text":"Now, there is a movement\nin the United States"},{"time":919705,"text":"of young people who I am very proud of\nwho are dealing with the structural issues"},{"time":926299,"text":"that need to change if we're going\nto be a better society."},{"time":930756,"text":"But there is this political ploy\nto try to pit police brutality"},{"time":935655,"text":"and police misconduct\nagainst black-on-black violence."},{"time":940693,"text":"But it's a fiction."},{"time":942597,"text":"It's all connected."},{"time":944617,"text":"When you think about decades\nof failed housing policies"},{"time":949331,"text":"and poor educational structures,"},{"time":953208,"text":"when you think about\npersistent unemployment"},{"time":956482,"text":"and underemployment in a community,"},{"time":959360,"text":"when you think about poor healthcare,"},{"time":962124,"text":"and then you throw drugs into the mix"},{"time":965300,"text":"and duffel bags full of guns,"},{"time":967348,"text":"little wonder that you would see\nthis culture of violence emerge."},{"time":972782,"text":"And then the response that comes\nfrom the state is more cops"},{"time":977140,"text":"and more suppression of hot spots."},{"time":980296,"text":"It's all connected,"},{"time":982562,"text":"and one of the wonderful things\nthat we've been able to do"},{"time":986340,"text":"is to be able to show the value\nof partnering together --"},{"time":991473,"text":"community, law enforcement,\nprivate sector, the city --"},{"time":997039,"text":"in order to reduce violence."},{"time":998427,"text":"You have to value\nthat community component."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002534,"text":"I believe that we can end\nthe era of violence in our cities."},{"time":1009154,"text":"I believe that it is possible\nand that people are doing it even now."},{"time":1015144,"text":"But I need your help."},{"time":1017537,"text":"It can't just come from folks\nwho are burning themselves out"},{"time":1022186,"text":"in the community."},{"time":1023744,"text":"They need support. They need help."},{"time":1026742,"text":"Go back to your city."},{"time":1028680,"text":"Find those people."},{"time":1030259,"text":"\"You need some help? I'll help you out.\""},{"time":1032976,"text":"Find those people. They're there."},{"time":1036180,"text":"Bring them together with law enforcement,\nthe private sector, and the city,"},{"time":1041537,"text":"with the one aim of reducing violence,"},{"time":1044400,"text":"but make sure that\nthat community component is strong."},{"time":1048346,"text":"Because the old adage\nthat comes from Burundi is right:"},{"time":1051667,"text":"that you do for me,\nwithout me, you do to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1059410,"text":"God bless you. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1061535,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}